BUGS
  - cut and the paste back doesn't yield the same results
  - cut shouldn't cut walls of bordering cells
  - left edge of spinner symbols is cut off on high zoom levels on retina screens
  - textfields: max length (note, ID field)
  - note dialog: first tab, tab x2, ID tab -> ID field is in edit mode
  - undo after cut/erase/etc selection should restore cursor to selection to
    left corner, not bottom right
  - drawlevel - pixel level drawing problems (also for regions)
  - turn off trail mode when changing the level via the dropwodn


